comments: Knowledgeable and extremely passionate about her interests but ultimately unavailable. Seems awesome for those to whom she\'s committed, but disappointing if you\'re on the outside looking in.

She is my adviser and she\'s awesome. One of the most passionate professors about what she does at the school. She is picky but she\'ll tend to write a lot of comments on your paper but still give you a good grade.

she\'s a cool person and i really like her outside of the classroom. but her class is pretty hard, even for envi sci majors. subject matter is interesting though and you can tell she\'s passionate and knows everything. unclear about grading and demanding about small details

I have a personal interest in Environmental Studies and I like the class. One problem with the class is that the lab assignments are vague and she is a hard grader. If you don\'t go to class, she\'ll notice and she\'ll treat you differently. Also, pretend that you\'re interested in the subject, or she won\'t be interested in you. Pay attention in class!
